libxc
------------------------------------------
libxc is a library of exchange and correlation functionals. Its purpose is to
be used in codes that implement density-functional theory. For the moment, the
library includes most of the local density approximations (LDAs), generalized
density approximation (GGAs), and meta-GGAs. The library provides values for
the energy density and its 1st, 2nd, and (for the LDAs) 3rd derivatives.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.10.0-1
  libgfortran3-6.4.0-5
  libxc-devel-4.0.4-1bl1
  libxc5-4.0.4-1bl1
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-10-1
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.6.2-1
  cygport-0.31.0-1
  gcc-core-6.4.0-5
  gcc-fortran-6.4.0-5
  libtool-2.4.6-5
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  http://octopus-code.org/wiki/Libxc

Canonical download:
  https://gitlab.com/libxc/libxc/repository/4.0.4/archive.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libxc-4.0.4-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libxc-4.0.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libxc-4.0.4-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libxc-4.0.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libxc5-4.0.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libxc-devel-4.0.4-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libxc)
  /usr/bin/xc-info.exe
  /usr/bin/xc-threshold.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libxc.README
  /usr/share/doc/libxc/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libxc/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libxc/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libxc/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libxc/README
  /usr/share/doc/libxc/TODO

(libxc5)
  /usr/bin/cygxc-5.dll
  /usr/bin/cygxcf03-5.dll
  /usr/bin/cygxcf90-5.dll

(libxc-devel)
  /usr/include/libxc_funcs_m.mod
  /usr/include/xc.h
  /usr/include/xc_f03_lib_m.mod
  /usr/include/xc_f90_lib_m.mod
  /usr/include/xc_f90_types_m.mod
  /usr/include/xc_funcs.h
  /usr/include/xc_funcs_removed.h
  /usr/include/xc_version.h
  /usr/lib/libxc.dll.a
  /usr/lib/libxcf03.dll.a
  /usr/lib/libxcf90.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libxc.pc

